{
  "page": "Pyramid of Yherizan",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rhaegal.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/ba/Rhaegal.jpg/300px-Rhaegal.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"393\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/ba/Rhaegal.jpg/450px-Rhaegal.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/ba/Rhaegal.jpg/600px-Rhaegal.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rhaegal.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegal\" title=\"Rhaegal\">Rhaegal</a> roosts on top of the pyramid of Yherizan.<br />Art by Robert O'Leary</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>pyramid of Yherizan</b> is a great black <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid\" title=\"Pyramid\">pyramid</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> and the home to members of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Yherizan\" title=\"House of Yherizan\">House of Yherizan</a>. The pyramid can been seen from the <a href=\"/index.php/Queen%27s_apartments_(Great_Pyramid)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen&#39;s apartments (Great Pyramid)\">Great Pyramid's terrace</a>.   \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Yherizan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Yherizan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After being unleashed with his brother <a href=\"/index.php/Viserion\" title=\"Viserion\">Viserion</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegal\" title=\"Rhaegal\">Rhaegal</a> makes his lair in the pyramid of Yherizan, forcing the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Yherizan\" title=\"House of Yherizan\">House of Yherizan</a> to abandon their home.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Yherizan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The rain had drowned the worst of the fires, but wisps of smoke still rose from the smoldering ruin that had been the <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid_of_Hazkar\" title=\"Pyramid of Hazkar\">pyramid of Hazkar</a>, and the great black pyramid of Yherizan where <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegal\" title=\"Rhaegal\">Rhaegal</a> had made his lair hulked in the gloom like a fat woman bedecked with glowing orange jewels.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Yherizan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 70\">Chapter 70</a>, The Queen's Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403120628\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: